---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../config/site";

const title = "Privacy Policy";
const description = "Privacy Policy for Ethyl Merc Group — how we collect, use and protect your information.";
const lastUpdated = "February 2025";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-10 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          Ethyl Merc Group Limited ("EMG", "we", "us", or "our") is a New Zealand-registered company providing facilities management and trade services. Our registered office is in Auckland, New Zealand. You can contact us at <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.contact.email}`} class="text-accent hover:underline">{siteConfig.contact.email}</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect personal information that you provide directly to us, including when you:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Submit an enquiry or contact form on our website</li>
          <li>Request a quote or use our Pre-Qualification Wizard</li>
          <li>Apply to become a trade partner</li>
          <li>Call or email us directly</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">This may include your name, email address, phone number, company name, property address, and the nature of your enquiry.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">We may also collect non-personal data through cookies and analytics tools (such as page views, browser type, and referral source) to improve our website performance.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Respond to your enquiry or service request</li>
          <li>Prepare and deliver quotes</li>
          <li>Manage our trade partner onboarding process</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
          <li>Comply with our legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">4. Disclosure of Your Information</h2>
        <p>We may share your information with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Trade partners within the EMG collective</strong> — to fulfil your service request</li>
          <li><strong>Service providers</strong> — including IT, hosting, and communication platforms that support our operations, under confidentiality agreements</li>
          <li><strong>Regulatory authorities</strong> — where required by law</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some website functionality.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">6. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes for which it was collected, or as required by law. Enquiry records are typically retained for 7 years for accounting and audit purposes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the New Zealand Privacy Act 2020, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Ask us to delete your information (subject to legal obligations)</li>
          <li>Make a complaint to the Office of the Privacy Commissioner</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.contact.email}`} class="text-accent hover:underline">{siteConfig.contact.email}</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">8. Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from loss, misuse, and unauthorised access. However, no internet transmission is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of our website constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-primary mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact:</p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-6 bg-neutral-light rounded-xl">
          <p class="font-bold text-primary">Ethyl Merc Group Limited</p>
          <p>{siteConfig.contact.address}</p>
          <p>Email: <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.contact.email}`} class="text-accent hover:underline">{siteConfig.contact.email}</a></p>
          <p>Phone: <a href={`tel:${siteConfig.contact.phone}`} class="text-accent hover:underline">{siteConfig.contact.phone}</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
